      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, representing the pinnacle of its class. This specimen remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that shows no signs of wear. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, this automobile offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
